folder: Otsego Street & Creamer Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Otsego Street(left) north from Creamer Street, showing the Red Hook Houses, a low rent government housing center, under construction on the north side of Lorraine Street. The entire block from Creamer to Lorraine Streets is an empty lot.
View 2 is north on Otsego Street, from a point nearer Lorraine Street.
April 19,1939
Views 1, 2

folder: Dikeman Street & Otsego Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Dikeman Street (left), north side, west from Otsego to Dwight Streets. On the right are Nos. 38 and 36 Otsego Street.
